@SSJason

In the version you posted you can test play your games for all of the target platforms, but exporting had not been implemented yet. You can update safely to the latest version where exporting should be enabled, but those modules simply haven't been cracked yet. If you find a way to update to the last version of the beta, I think they allowed exporting but with watermarks.

Looks like we're just going to have to wait for someone to crack 1.0.198, not 1.0.98
